{"tid":1847370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府帶頭罷工，你唔係仲返工呀 ?","createTime":"2020-01-28T04:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T04:59:07.000Z","uid":107023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0216c0e911dfd2938c8980f7d275b34b3836fbd","tid":1847370,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"政府宣布各部門在農曆新年假期後實施特別上班安排，除了提供緊急和必須公共服務的人員外，政府僱員在假期後無需返回寫字樓辦公，而是留在家中工作。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，有關安排是為了盡量減低疫情在社區擴散的風險，安排暫定實行至下月2日，政府屆時會再檢視情況，並呼籲私人機構在可行情況下，作類似安排。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次應該不論黃藍，都應該罷工/停工"},{"pid":"4ef48475713949080436c434a1544ddbc5a63ab9","tid":1847370,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"全港罷工"},{"pid":"878c42a730f9eb9b5eb6a453dd62cdfb71222715","tid":1847370,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">糧照出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5187fe4c8edf0b41ffa3358d76021e01738499c0","tid":1847370,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"878c42a730f9eb9b5eb6a453dd62cdfb71222715","tid":1847370,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">糧照出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"港共正仆街"}]}